list.comment: Made FileListing automatically not write Player or LargeDataMapping files if the output savefile is for a different console than the input. added static FileListing::AUTO_REMOVE_PLAYERS and FileListing::AUTO_REMOVE_DATA_MAPPING values, which are defaulted to true.
